comment._content: Colonel Arthur C. Lybarger (1904-1962). he was born in Ohio on August 7, 1904. He was married to Virginia (1912-2000). He died on December 19, 1962 in Minnesota. He was buried in Arlington National Cemetery . www.findagrave.com/cgi-bin/fg.cgi?page=gr&GRid=49250713
